{"items":{"4":{"ordinal":0,"content":"<p>Common<\/p>","type":"idea","parent":"root","treeType":"horizontal"},"root":{"type":"header","treeType":"horizontal"},"1":{"ordinal":1,"content":"<p>read_project<\/p>","type":"idea","parent":"root","treeType":"horizontal"},"5":{"ordinal":0,"content":"<p>Generate a JS module.<\/p><p>Use CommonJS format.<\/p><p>Generate all the necessary functions.<\/p><p>Do not add any dependencies to the module.<\/p><p>Do not use \"class\", \"new\", and \"this\" keywords.<\/p><p>Do not use object destructuring.<\/p><p>Add async\/await where necessary.<\/p><p>Use \"undefined\" instead of \"null\".<\/p><p>Do not use array.length = 0 trick.<\/p><p>Use plain JS objects for dictionaries and sets.<\/p><p>Use {} to create new dictionaries and sets.<\/p><p>Use \"in\" operator to check if a key is in the map or set.<\/p><p>Keep snake case identifier style where the specs follow it.<\/p><p>Report the errors instead of generating code if there are critical errors.<\/p>","w":155,"type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"4"},"2":{"ordinal":0,"content":"<p>Export <strong>read_project<\/strong> function.<\/p><p>Do not generate handles for created Nodes.<\/p>","w":155,"type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"1"},"6":{"ordinal":2,"content":"<p>generate_lua<\/p>","type":"idea","parent":"root","treeType":"horizontal"},"7":{"ordinal":0,"content":"<p>Generate <strong>generate_pfl<\/strong> Javascript function.<\/p><p>All other functions are already defined.<\/p><p>read_project is async<\/p><p>pause is async<\/p>","w":155,"type":"idea","parent":"6","treeType":"horizontal"},"3":{"ordinal":1,"content":"<p>Find error in the requirements for a JS function <strong>read_project<\/strong>.<\/p><p>Do not generate code.<\/p><p>Build a list of errors.<\/p>","w":155,"type":"idea","treeType":"horizontal","parent":"1"}},"type":"graf"}